INTRODUCTION
============
System for archiving log files onto Amazon S3.

INSTALLATION
============

PACKAGE INSTALL ( Recommended )
================================

The recommended way to install LogArchiveS3 is using your package manager, please see http://las3.niftiestsoftware.com/ for installation 
instructions.

SOURCE INSTALL
==============

Clone the git repo:

git clone git://github.com/simoncadman/LogArchiveS3.git

cd LogArchiveS3/
./configure
make install
